></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-315_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-317_">Pay attention to your clients.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-318_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-320_">Consider the long term; a client is for life.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-fKVqWL bSBlpa pf-321_"><button type="button" class="sc-hGPBjI jBRLdO pf-322_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="be15cac7-6414-48f1-8cde-baae7e90299f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How does technology influence customer service experience?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="be15cac7-6414-48f1-8cde-baae7e90299f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-dlVxhl fcYZSZ pf-324_"><div class="sc-dPiLbb jGEmDy pf-325_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-326_"><p class="sc-dwsnSq jqylDz pf-327_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-329_">Technology is a collection of techniques. Technology is not only a tool a company should have when it comes to customer service—it is a crucial component. Enabling effective and efficient service delivery, resulting in new customer support experiences.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-fKVqWL bSBlpa pf-330_"><button type="button" class="sc-hGPBjI jBRLdO pf-331_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="debaae7e-9029-4fa6-91b4-20554581e373" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the advantages of social media in business?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="debaae7e-9029-4fa6-91b4-20554581e373" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-dlVxhl fcYZSZ pf-333_"><div class="sc-dPiLbb jGEmDy pf-334_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-335_"><p class="sc-dwsnSq jqylDz pf-336_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-338_">These are the advantages of social media in business:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-339_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-340_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-342_">Relatively low marketing costs.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-343_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-345_">Increase brand awareness and sales.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-346_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-348_">Increase website traffic and improve rankings on search engines.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-349_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-351_">Cost-effective lead generation.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-352_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-354_">Opportunity to build customer relationships.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-355_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-357_">Possibility to conduct market research about your customers.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-358_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-360_">Improve networking.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-fKVqWL bSBlpa pf-361_"><button type="button" class="sc-hGPBjI jBRLdO pf-362_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="b4205545-81e3-43a2-9068-8b9398037c54" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the disadvantages of social media in business?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b4205545-81e3-43a2-9068-8b9398037c54" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-dlVxhl fcYZSZ pf-364_"><div class="sc-dPiLbb jGEmDy pf-365_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-366_"><p class="sc-dwsnSq jqylDz pf-367_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-369_">These are the disadvantages of social media in business:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-370_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-371_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-373_">Risk of lousy publicity.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-374_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-376_">It could be necessary to use more resources to manage your internet presence.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-377_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-379_">Requires regular monitoring.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-380_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-382_">It will only benefit your company if you actively work your social media presence. </span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-383_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-385_">Risk of unwanted or inappropriate behaviour from social media trolls.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-386_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-388_">Increasing online exposure can potentially attract threats like information leaks or hacking.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-fKVqWL bSBlpa pf-389_"><button type="button" class="sc-hGPBjI jBRLdO pf-390_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="688b9398-037c-44f2-a96e-d59ceb079614" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the benefits of using social media for customer service?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="688b9398-037c-44f2-a96e-d59ceb079614" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-dlVxhl fcYZSZ pf-392_"><div class="sc-dPiLbb jGEmDy pf-393_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-394_"><p class="sc-dwsnSq jqylDz pf-395_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-397_">The five benefits of utilising social media for customer service are the following:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-398_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-399_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-401_">Everyone has adopted it</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-402_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-404_">24/7 customer service option</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-405_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-407_">Additional interaction options</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-408_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-410_">Management of crises efficiently</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-411_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-413_">Knowledge of how to sell goods and services.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-fKVqWL bSBlpa pf-414_"><button type="button" class="sc-hGPBjI jBRLdO pf-415_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="79f71489-1c4a-4af3-a66b-16e814f41180" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the five core principles of customer service?
