</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-eWfVMQ HLdwB pf-430_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-432_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Accountability </span>- Create team-wide responsibility for customer service.
